      {
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "text": "Name of Local Body issuing Certificate : Thiruvananthapuram Corporation",
                "style": "title-header"
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },{
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "text": "ജനന സർട്ടിഫിക്കറ്റ്",
                "style": "title-header"
              },
              {
                "text": " ",
                "width": "1%"
              },
              {
                "text": "BIRTH CERTIFICATE",
                "style": "title-header"
              },
              {
                "text": " ",
                "width": "1%"
              },
              {
                "text": "(Issued Under Section 12)",
                "style": "title-header"
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },
      {
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "text": "(1967-ലെ ജനന-മരണ രജിസ്‌ട്രേഷൻ ആക്ടിലെ 12-ാം വകുപ്പും 1999-ലെ കേരള ജനന-മരണ രജിസ്ട്രേഷന് ചട്ടങ്ങളിലെ 8-ാംചാട്ടവും അനുസരിച്ചു നൽകുന്നത്.)",
                    "style": "rule-header"
                  }
                ]

              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },
      {
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "text": "(Issued Under Section 12/17 of the Registration of Births and Deaths Act, 1969 and Rule8/13 the Testing Registration of Births and Deaths Rules,1999)",
                    "style": "rule-header"
                  }
                ]

              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },
      {
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "text": ["താഴെ പറയുന്ന വിവരങ്ങൾ കേരള  സംസ്‌ഥാനത്തിലെ തിരുവനന്തപുരം ജില്ലയിലെ തിരുവനന്തപുരം താലൂക്കിലെ തിരുവനന്തപുരം കോർപ്പറേഷൻ -ലെ ( തദേശസ്ഥാപനം) അസ്സൽ ജനന രജിസ്റ്ററിൽ നിന്ന് എടുത്തിട്ടുള്ളവയാണെന്ന് സാക്ഷ്യപ്പെടുത്തുന്നു ."],
                    "style": "rule-body_multiLang"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },

      {
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "text": "This is to certify that the following information has been taken from the original record of birth which is the register for (local area/localbody) Thiruvananthapuram Corporation of Taluk Thiruvananthapuram of District Thiruvananthapuram of State Kerala.",
                    "style": "rule-body_multiLang"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },

      {
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "text": "പേര്/NAME: {{name}}",
                    "width": "49%",
                    "style": "details-body"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " ",
                    "width": "1%"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "ആൺ/പെൺ/SEX: {{gender}}",
                    "style": "details-body"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            [
              {
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "text": "ജനന തീയതി/DATE OF BIRTH: {{dob}}",
