                "text": "ഓരോ ജനനവും മരണവും രജിസ്റ്റർ ചെയ്തുവെന്ന് ഉറപ്പുവരുത്തുക.",
                "style": "footer"
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      },{
        "style": "ws-head",
        "table": {
          "widths": ["*"],
          "body": [
            [
              {
                "text": "This certificate is computer generated and does not require any Seal/Signature in original The Govt. vide G.O.(Ms) No.202/2012/LSGD dated 25/07/2012 has approved this certificate as a valid document for all official purposes Authenticity of this certificate can be verified at www.cr.lsgkerala.gov.in. The Key Number is unique to each event.,      Software developed and supported by Information Kerala Mission                    Certificate printed before the last updated date is invalid",
                "style": "footer"
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        "layout": "noBorders"
      }
